  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets the pipeline's diffuse color, in the standard OpenGL lighting
model. The diffuse color is most intense where the light hits the
surface directly - perpendicular to the surface.</p>  <p>The default value is (0.8, 0.8, 0.8, 1.0)</p>
  <p>Since 2.0</p>
